17518       // RedOp1 = select i1 ?, i1 LHS, i1 false
17519       // RedOp2 = select i1 RHS, i1 ?, i1 false
17520 
17521       // Then, we swap LHS/RHS to create a new op that matches the poison
17522       // semantics of the original code.
17523 
